Invocation Name: starship captain quiz
des:
Just five yes/no questions to answer and you will know who your role model is when it comes to sitting in the captain's chair of a fabulous spaceship! See if you come after the legends of the starships Enterprise, Serenity, NSEA Protector or the Battlestar Pegasus. 

No special hardware needed, although minor multimodal support is included.
